entity.lycanitesmobs.aspid.name=Aspid
entity.lycanitesmobs.aspid.description=Peaceful reptiles with strange growths on their backs. Aspids love mushrooms and can be farmed with them. Be careful however as they constantly emit a cloud of poison and usually leave a trail of this behind them.
entity.lycanitesmobs.aspid.habitat=These creatures are usually found in swamps, dark forests and mushroom islands due to their love of the shroom!
entity.lycanitesmobs.aspid.combat=Aspids are usually peaceful but the poisonous clouds they emit can be quite dangerous, these don't stop passionate farmers however!